
"Still, those two seem quite rude. Calling me a low-life." Haruka muttered under his breath, with the only clothing he had was the towel wrapped tightly around his waist.
"They're royalty Haruka. They act like the Celestial Dragons. I guess its natural." Aya explained whilst in the shower.
"But we should be glad that Princess Twilight stood up for us otherwise Haruka would've slice their ass." Sakura noted her mouth full of the chocolate biscuits that the walls were made of.
"Stop eating would ya!" They shouted after Aya slapped her.
Then an explosion was heard......